headline: Keysight Announces Executive Leadership Transitions and New Appointments
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., May 27, 2025--Keysight Technologies, Inc. (NYSE: KEYS), today announced two executive leadership appointments that underscore the company’s legacy of developing strong leaders with a focus on innovation, talent development, and operational excellence.
